{"tid":830174,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚青山道被捕 或將終身監禁","createTime":"2018-09-21T03:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T08:57:12.000Z","uid":163207,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f343f1f656db52a95d5373f061f42f02d2a37b97","tid":830174,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180404/bkn-20180404034219969-0404_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180404%2Fbkn-20180404034219969-0404_00822_001.html&d=P5LHX3D3HIDgOzZmlaQVvQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=63d859ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180404/bkn-20180404034219969-0404_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n深水埗警區特別職務隊根據線報及經深入調查後，昨（3日）晚約11時進行打擊毒品行動，突擊搜查長沙灣青山道296號一單位。行動中，警員在單位內檢獲約22克懷疑「冰」毒、約15克懷疑海洛英、約3克懷疑可卡因及一批毒品包裝工具，毒品總值約3萬2千港元。單位內一名54歲姓李本地男子涉嫌「販毒」被捕，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，販毒屬嚴重罪行，根據香港法例第134章《危險藥物條例》，一經定罪，最高可判處罰款5百萬港元及終身監禁，市民切勿以身試法。"},{"pid":"09a8a1157ce95f82ccb7ec984e58a07851baf100","tid":830174,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"04月04日"},{"pid":"65e1001d9d6e2d1e50e16d15c322aed70eab0c58","tid":830174,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09a8a1157ce95f82ccb7ec984e58a07851baf100","tid":830174,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"04月04日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"兒童節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9e1a2a5fd9e565fcba33d336fac44e2ac66df7","tid":830174,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"4個低置仔報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}